{
  "text": "The higher MCS for students living with parents contrasts the findings of a study in the Netherlands, [CITATION_1] where students living with parents reported a lower general health status. The poor score of students living in the medical school hostel on the environmental domain reiterates the call for better living conditions in Indian hostels.",
